{
  "texts": [
    "Our two next research questions were thus:",
    "RQ2: What is the correlation between readability and userperceived quality of the stimuli?",
    "RQ3: Do participants rate the quality of text written by an AI differently from that of text written by a human?",
    "Testing whether humans can tell the difference between a human and a machine is often referred to as a Turing Test.",
    "Alan Turing proposed the Imitation Game method in 1950 to test whether machines can think (Turing, 1950)."
  ]
}